{"tid":697670,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"建議咁多位受政治迫害嘅義士入到去要繼續讀書","createTime":"2018-06-11T06:04:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-05T05:34:15.000Z","uid":15935,"like":20,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e61703642fdc7d405e773a06f776c6c4e2d87e7c","tid":697670,"uid":15935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T06:04:54.000Z","msg":"米已成炊，港共政府唔會比你好過，應該點都要坐咁多碌，無咗黃金時段嘅人生...<br />\n只係希望你地可以用盡埋呢個政權嘅資源，為自己考更高級嘅學歷，當係裝備自己又好/有啲嘢寄托都好，個幾年時間真係好長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ae31728135ac24e11e7bf700ec0f2589a6198e6","tid":697670,"uid":15935,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T06:15:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9ab4ea337e90d91d742c8493f46ead9aae37813","tid":697670,"uid":15935,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T12:50:42.000Z","msg":"梁天琦：<br />\n<br />\n本土民主前線前發言人梁天琦因為2016年旺角騷亂，被裁定暴動罪成，判入獄6年，目前正就暴動罪定罪及刑期提出上訴。<br />\n<br />\n梁天琦稱在獄中生活一切安好，並指石壁監獄的伙食比在荔枝角收押時理想；石壁監獄的職員都鼓勵他繼續進修，梁已決定在獄中再修讀第二個學士學位，科目為社會科學。<br />\n<br />\n梁天琦除決心在獄中戒煙，大學主修哲學的他，平日在獄中閱讀的均是英文書，當中包括著名法國哲學家沙特著名劇作《密室》（Huis-clos)。"},{"pid":"3f5a81cdff2fb2b58148efef755f9a34c73d3297","tid":697670,"uid":15935,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T12:51:29.000Z","msg":"盧建民<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/04/205126_2f96a1d8a4303b8de47983822c776bfc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F04%2F205126_2f96a1d8a4303b8de47983822c776bfc.png&h=9676d539&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"924800cb027a2362ff3b2d3a7f546c685d02aa3d","tid":697670,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T13:06:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"13fdcb13162d0452bf17146d9478b3f2fff2c6d6","tid":697670,"uid":141151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"924800cb027a2362ff3b2d3a7f546c685d02aa3d","tid":697